DataAttributes.Adjustment: Describes whether and how the provided earnings have been adjusted for factors such as inflation, participant demographics and economic conditions.

DataNotAvailable.Description: Number of credential AggregateDataProfile in the reporting group for which employment and earnings data has not been included in the data set

DemographicEarningsRate.Description: Earnings rate for a demographic category.

DemographicEmploymentRate.Description: Employment rate for a demographic category.

DataAttributes.EarningsDefinition: Definition of "earnings" used by the data source in the context of the reporting group.
DataAttributes.EmploymentDefinition: Statement of criteria used to determine whether sufficient levels of work time and/or earnings have been met to be considered employed during the earning time period.

EmploymentRate.Description: Rate computed by dividing the number of holders or subjects meeting the data set's criteria of employment (meetEmploymentCriteria) by the number of holders or subjects for which data was available (dataAvailable).

IndustryRate.Description: Employment rate for an industry category.

InsufficientEmploymentCriteria.Description: Number of holders that do not meet the prescribed employment threshold in terms of earnings or time engaged in work as defined for the data set.

MeetEmploymentCriteria.Description: Number of holders that meet the prescribed employment threshold in terms of earnings or time engaged in work as defined for the data set.

NonCompleters.Description: Non-holders who departed or are likely to depart higher education prematurely.

NonHoldersInSet.Description: Non-holder subject actively pursuing the credential through a program or assessment.

OccupationRate.Description: Employment rate for an occupation category.

RegionalEarningsDistribution.Description: Reference to an entity describing median earnings as well as earnings at various percentiles for holders or subjects in the region.

RegionalEmploymentRate.Description: Reference to an entity describing median earnings as well as earnings at various percentiles for holders or subjects in the region.

RelatedEmployment.Description: Number of people employed in the area of work (e.g., industry, occupation) in which the credential provided preparation.

SubjectsInSet.Description: Total credential holders and non-holders in the final data collection and reporting.

SufficientEmploymentCriteria.Description: Number of holders that meet the prescribed employment threshold in terms of earnings or time engaged in work as defined for the data set

UnrelatedEmployment.Description: Number of people employed outside the area of work (e.g., industry, occupation) in which the credential provided preparation.

DataAttributes.WorkTimeThreshold: Statement of earnings thresholds used in determining whether a sufficient level of workforce attachment has been achieved to qualify as employed during the chosen employment and earnings time period.
